Ideally located within the last-mile industrial precinct of Chullora, these brand new facilities present an exceptional opportunity to secure an A-grade warehouse within one of Sydney’s most sought-after locations.

Chullora is located within Sydney’s inner west region, which is an established precinct that benefits from excellent transportation connectivity to Sydney’s major arterial routes.

+ Flexible areas of 3,800sqm, 4,735sqm and up to 6,235sqm
+ Combination of docks and on-grade doors
+ Ability to install chillers and temperature controlled areas
+ 10m+ internal warehouse clearance
+ Excellent exposure to Hume Highway and Centenary Drive
+ Less than 3km to Australia Post
+ 3km to the M4 Motorway 
+ 9km to the M5 Motorway
+ 13km to Sydney CBD
+ 16km to Port Botany



For more information, please contact the listed CBRE agents.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Located within the highly sought after and tightly held industrial precinct, this iconic estate will appeal to users seeking a location in Sydney’s Inner West with access to key road infrastructure. 

Only 5km to the M4 Motorway and 6km to the M4 Motorway, Chullora Logistics Park affords efficient access to the north and the south respectively. The estate is within 17km from the Sydney CBD and within proximity to key population densities, strong labour markets and the recently completed Enfield Intermodal Terminal.

Various configurations are available with areas from 3,000sqm to12,000sqm* for pre-lease. The size and specifications of the facilities can be tailored to meet the end user’s needs. 

Building 1 Features:
• Prime industrial facility of approximately 3,500sqm
• Minimum 10.5m internal clearance
• Combination of 2 recessed docks and 3 on-grade doors
• B-double designed access and generous truck marshalling
• ESFR Fire Suppression System
• Massive exposure to approximately 44,000 vehicles per day and the Hume Highway
• Ability to tailor temperature control and racking requirements
• ESD Initiatives including rain water harvesting, ventilation, solar and LED lighting
• Join neighbours including Australia Post, Lion Nathan, Primo Smallgoods and EWE Global Express.

Building 4 Features:
• Prime industrial facility can accommodate users from 4,000m2 up 11,523m2
• Minimum 10.5m internal clearance
• Combination of recessed docks and on-grade doors
• B-double designed access and generous truck marshalling
• ESFR Fire Suppression System
• Flexible office space with separate car parking entrances
• Ability to tailor temperature control and racking requirements
• ESD Initiatives including rain water harvesting, ventilation, solar and LED lighting
• Join neighbours including Australia Post, Lion Nathan, Primo Smallgoods and EWE Global Express.

Should you require an Information Memorandum or wish to discuss this opportunity further, please don’t hesitate to contact the exclusive leasing agents.
